 \frac{e^h - 1}{h} = \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{h^{n-1}}{n!} = 1 + \sum_{n = 2}^{\infty} \frac{h^{n-1}}{n!} \to 1 \text{ as } h\to 0. 
